sentences: He worked with conductor Kent Nagano in producing concerts for the Festspiel Plus in Munich, Germany.
From 2008 to 2015, he produced a multi-genre performance series at the Broad Stage in Santa Monica, California.
Wendell has taught jazz USC and the New School in New York City.
